A street play has been on since January 10 as part of the week-long road safety awareness programmes in the city.Fifteen students from St. Paulâ€™s College, CUSAT Centre for Legal Studies, and Thrissur Law College participated in the street play. The play focussed on problems of people who ride motor cycles without wearing helmets and drivers not using seat belts. The valedictory function of the week-long programme was held at the Vyttila Mobility Hub on Saturday. The programme was organised by the Motor Vehicles Department.